ast.name: turtle triangle spiral
ast.comment: A turtle program that draws triangles into a colored spiral.

body.text: Edit this action to create your own turtle drawings.
Change the code below to draw your own patterns.
Turn a little and draw a triangle
Don't forget to publish your turtle drawing!!
On each step, move by 100 pixels

sj4JaXLfp8ofkaWBydpZ9ZQt.text: We are going to draw triangle if increasing sizes and different colors.

WOIHVTAVjrdYjybmfziHTLEa.text: Creates the trutle and wakes it up!

xOpdpXcyMR8REg5W0eNZfIsX.text: Create the bitmap where the turtle will paint

qHrWpelV0ZGDMOFOXH66SO8B.text: Sets the pen down to enable the turtle to draw as it moves.

VCZREW2SXB93BtnRgNuU4FRA.text: Lifts the pen up to stop drawing as the turtle moves.

JcbS9shwDFdfKu56YYYp48Y8.text: Turns and moves the turtle to the specified location. If the pen is down, it will draw a line as it moves.

PMQwBaBiD2RQAx9LgvGVSAWF.text: Moves the turtle to a specified distance. If the pen is down, it will draw a line as it moves.

FM63IK4MEnHEMS7aGlKq6JUV.text: Turns the turtle by the specified angle. Angle is in degrees and can be either positive or negative. If the angle is positive, the turtle turns to its right. If it is negative, the turtle turns to its left.

f4s3pLsqoho4u95gldUveP1K.text: Sets the color of the pen.

YTjkdEMTk4ThvZVbcje7L42p.text: Maps the world coordinates to the board coordinates.

NdwDVrrOYxn2McHmqevfISEm.text: Returns the x coordinate of the turtle.

rKclBfclC2F7TWW46cZLbmhn.text: Returns the y coordinate of the turtle.

xEneGadCRT2x4dpGX4Jj8vHq.text: Returns the angle of the turtle.

xZe2081DYT7Rvupj4so4ejex.text: Picks a color around the color spectrum.
